Title: Dynamic host management: Fix MKAPIError
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1652680704
Edition: cee
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b09

If the global option "Connection to the Web API" was changed, the error
"MKAPIError: {"title": "You need to be authenticated to use the REST API.",
"status": 401}" occurred.
